.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E9%85%B6%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%B6%E4%BF%83%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94/</guid><description>&lt;p>酶是催化特定反应的蛋白质（大部分），是一种生物催化剂。酶能通过降低反应的活化能加快反应速率，但&lt;mark>不改变反应的平衡点&lt;/mark>。酶具有催化效率高、&lt;mark>专一性强&lt;/mark>、&lt;mark>作用条件温和&lt;/mark>等特点。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>脂质代谢</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%84%82%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 13 Apr 2023 22:33:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%84%82%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</guid><description/></item><item><title>胆固醇代谢</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%84%82%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/%E8%83%86%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jul 2023 11:20:47 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%84%82%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/%E8%83%86%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</guid><description/></item><item><title>蛋白质消化吸收和氨基酸代谢</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E8%B4%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%8C%96%E5%90%B8%E6%94%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%A8%E5%9F%BA%E9%85%B8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 13 Apr 2023 21:23:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E8%B4%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%8C%96%E5%90%B8%E6%94%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%A8%E5%9F%BA%E9%85%B8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肝的生物化学</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8